title: [Incubation Terms] DeFi Options DAO
body:
**Project:** DeFi Options DAO (the “**Project**”)

# Motivation:
Due to successful optimization of core contracts deployment costs & lower than expected price of code audit, we reached significantly lower capital requirements for seed sale.

# Proposal:
The Project proposes to allocate 5% (instead of 10%) of the Project's total token supply for an initial seed-sale, raising a total amount of approximately $75,000 (instead of $150,000).

# Remaining Key Terms
The remaining Key Terms covering Token Allocation to ShineDAO, and Core Team Allocation along with Incubation, Withdrawal Rights and Vesting Period remain unchanged. Please refer to: https://snapshot.org/#/shinedao.eth/proposal/Qme9KsKww17XXFjnPDgwV1Wbvf6RnPL2sLwpzw3oqm3Qcs
author: 0xb1D92EEec6f9F224ABD294DE643C94A01cB14E51
